WEBVTT

00:00.500 --> 00:04.500
Welcome to team management.

00:05.700 --> 00:14.700
Invite members. Send email invitations to technicians, administrators, and client contacts, each with a role.

00:15.700 --> 00:24.700
Assign roles. Control permissions precisely — View Only for clients, Edit for technicians, Admin for managers, Owner for full control.

00:25.700 --> 00:35.000
Licences. Manage your seats — add or remove members, transfer licences, and monitor usage from the admin panel.
